  "hint": "K-map analysis: segment A is OFF only for digits 1 (001) and 4 (100). Notice that B₂ XOR B₀ = 1 exactly for those two inputs. So segment A = B₁ OR NOT(B₂ XOR B₀) = B₁ + (B₂ XNOR B₀). Use XOR, NOT, and OR.",
